title: #357: Fun Bucks (Bill Ottman)
itunes:title: Fun Bucks with Bill Ottman
description: Bill Ottman came over to my apartment to try his best to get the idea of crypto currency through my fat skull. For a Jew, it's almost shocking how little I understand about monetary things like this.
